{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"5b59c0f8-bb07-4478-a551-4f8c943e3ae0","content":"Here's what you need:\n\n### Environment Variables\n\nFor NativeAOT, `createdump` isn't bundled with the runtime, so you must explicitly set `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath`. Add these env vars and a volume for dump storage:\n\n```yaml\n# Pod spec changes\nspec:\n  containers:\n    - name: your-app\n      env:\n        # Enable automatic crash dump generation\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n          value: \"1\"\n        # Dump type: 1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage, 4=Full\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n          value: \"4\"\n        # Path to createdump (required for NativeAOT — not bundled in runtime)\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath\n          value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n        # Dump output path (%d = PID, %t = timestamp)\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n          value: \"/tmp/dumps/coredump.%d.%t\"\n      securityContext:\n        capabilities:\n          add:\n            # Required for createdump to ptrace the crashing process\n            - SYS_PTRACE\n      volumeMounts:\n        - name: crash-dumps\n          mountPath: /tmp/dumps\n  volumes:\n    - name: crash-dumps\n      emptyDir:\n        sizeLimit: 2Gi\n```\n\n### Key points\n\n- **`SYS_PTRACE`** — required; `createdump` uses `ptrace` to read process memory.\n- **`DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath`** — critical for NativeAOT since there's no bundled CoreCLR runtime to find it automatically.\n- **`MiniDumpType=4`** (Full) gives the most detail but produces large files. Use `2` (Heap) for a smaller but still useful dump.\n- **`emptyDir`** — swap to a `PersistentVolumeClaim` if you need dumps to survive pod restarts. With `emptyDir`, retrieve dumps before the pod is evicted (e.g., via a sidecar or `kubectl cp`).\n- Optionally set `DOTNET_CreateDumpDiagnostics=1` to get diagnostic logging from `createdump` itself to stderr.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2f9ad8b2-223b-4154-bac6-20e7f031ea56","outputTokens":585,"requestId":"A0CD:6C08C:A20B3A:C44694:6A01367F"},"id":"b20e7386-45c1-4229-b36f-2fbe13fd7fab","timestamp":"2026-05-11T01:53:15.222Z","parentId":"674ef3b4-7330-46f9-b18e-2eaea13160cc"}
